---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { APP_STORE_URL } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title="Support"
      description="Get help with ColorLenz. Answers to common questions about installation, presets, Privacy Mode, and more."
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <div class="container page-wrap">

        <header class="page-header">
          <div class="section-label">Help & FAQ</div>
          <h1>Support</h1>
          <p class="page-intro">
            Quick answers to common questions. If something isn't here,
            <a href="mailto:pieternatanael@icloud.com">send us a note</a>.
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="faq-sections">

          <div class="faq-group">
            <h2>Getting started</h2>
            <dl class="faq-list">

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>What's free and what's paid?</dt>
                <dd>
                  The app is free to download and use with the default settings, no account,
                  no time limit. The floating lens works, Privacy Mode works, and your screen
                  starts feeling better immediately.<br /><br />
                  For <strong>$0.99/month</strong> you unlock full personalization: all 7 mood
                  presets, 14 pill themes, and the custom preset builder. You can cancel anytime
                  from your Mac App Store subscriptions.
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>How do I install ColorLenz?</dt>
                <dd>
                  Download it from the <a href={APP_STORE_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mac App Store</a>.
                  Once installed, open the app, it lives in your menu bar and starts working immediately.
                  No account, no setup required.
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>Is ColorLenz really free?</dt>
                <dd>
                  Yes, the core app is free, forever. You can download it and use it with the default
                  settings at no cost, with no time limit. Personalization features (mood presets, pill
                  themes, custom presets) are unlocked with a $0.99/month subscription.
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>What macOS version do I need?</dt>
                <dd>
                  ColorLenz requires macOS 13 (Ventura) or later. It's optimized for Apple Silicon but
                  runs great on Intel Macs too.
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>Will ColorLenz slow down my computer?</dt>
                <dd>
                  No. ColorLenz is designed to be lightweight. It uses a compositing layer that
                  works with your display hardware rather than intercepting every frame, so CPU and
                  battery impact are minimal.
                </dd>
              </div>

            </dl>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-group">
            <h2>Using the app</h2>
            <dl class="faq-list">

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>What are the seven presets?</dt>
                <dd>
                  Cold Sheep, Brain Power, Caramel Slice, Curious Alpaca, Foggy Mind,
                  Sick Rooster, and Tiger Toast. Each one is a carefully tuned combination of
                  color temperature, tint, and contrast. The best way to understand them is to
                  try them, they're designed to feel intuitive once you experience them.
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>Can I create my own presets?</dt>
                <dd>
                  Yes. Use the Custom Presets feature to dial in your own filter combination and
                  give it a name you'll actually remember.
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>What are the 14 pill themes?</dt>
                <dd>
                  Pill themes change the visual style of the ColorLenz floating interface itself,
                  think of it as choosing a case for your lens. They don't affect the color filter,
                  just how the app looks on screen.
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>How does Privacy Mode work?</dt>
                <dd>
                  Privacy Mode wraps your screen in a dark overlay, instantly obscuring your content
                  from anyone nearby. One tap to activate, one tap to dismiss. It's designed for
                  public spaces, shared offices, or any moment you need a second of visual quiet.
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>Does ColorLenz work with all apps?</dt>
                <dd>
                  Yes. The floating lens works on top of any app or window, browsers, editors,
                  video players, design tools, everything. A small number of full-screen video
                  games that bypass the system compositor may be unaffected.
                </dd>
              </div>

            </dl>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-group">
            <h2>Windows &amp; other platforms</h2>
            <dl class="faq-list">

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>Is there a Windows version?</dt>
                <dd>
                  Not yet.</a> and
                 
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>What about iOS or iPadOS?</dt>
                <dd>
                  Not planned at the moment. We're focused on getting the desktop experience
                  right before expanding to other platforms.
                </dd>
              </div>

            </dl>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-group">
            <h2>Privacy &amp; data</h2>
            <dl class="faq-list">

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>Does ColorLenz collect any data about me?</dt>
                <dd>
                  No. ColorLenz does not collect, store, or transmit personal data. It runs
                  entirely on your device. See our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for
                  the full details.
                </dd>
              </div>

              <div class="faq-item">
                <dt>Does it require an internet connection?</dt>
                <dd>
                  No. ColorLenz works fully offline. An internet connection is only needed
                  to download the app from the Mac App Store.
                </dd>
              </div>

            </dl>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="contact-block">
          <h3>Still have a question?</h3>
          <p>
            We're a small team and we genuinely read every message. Reach out at{' '}
            <a href="mailto:pieternatanael@icloud.com">hello@colorlenz.com</a> or leave feedback below.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Feedback form -->
        <div class="feedback-block" id="feedback">
          <div class="feedback-header">
            <h3>Leave feedback</h3>
            <p>Name and email are optional, say as much or as little as you like.</p>
          </div>

          <form class="feedback-form" id="feedback-form">
            <input type="hidden" name="form_type" value="feedback" />

            <div class="form-row">
              <div class="form-field">
                <label for="feedback-name">Name <span class="optional">optional</span></label>
                <input type="text" id="feedback-name" name="name" placeholder="Your name" autocomplete="name" />
              </div>
              <div class="form-field">
                <label for="feedback-email">Email <span class="optional">optional</span></label>
                <input type="email" id="feedback-email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" autocomplete="email" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="feedback-message">Feedback <span class="required">*</span></label>
              <textarea
                id="feedback-message"
                name="message"
                placeholder="What's on your mind? Bug, idea, kind word, all welcome."
                rows="5"
                required
              ></textarea>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Feedback</button>
          </form>

          <p class="feedback-success" id="feedback-success" aria-live="polite">
            Thanks, we read every message.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<script>
  const form = document.getElementById('feedback-form') as HTMLFormElement | null;
  const success = document.getElementById('feedback-success');

  form?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    const data = Object.fromEntries(new FormData(form).entries());

    try {
      const res = await fetch('https://formspree.io/f/mrejvron', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', Accept: 'application/json' },
        body: JSON.stringify(data),
      });

      if (res.ok) {
        form.style.display = 'none';
        if (success) success.style.display = 'block';
      }
    } catch {
      form.style.display = 'none';
      if (success) success.style.display = 'block';
    }
  });
</script>

<style>
  .page-wrap {
    max-width: 760px;
    padding-top: 4rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .page-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .faq-sections {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .faq-group h2 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.25rem 0;
  }

  .faq-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  dt {
    font-size: 0.97rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    cursor: default;
  }

  dd {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  dd a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .contact-block {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .contact-block h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .contact-block p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .contact-block a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  /* ── Feedback form ── */
  .feedback-block {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .feedback-header {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feedback-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .feedback-header p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .feedback-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .form-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .form-field {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  .form-field label {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .optional {
    font-weight: 400;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .required {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .form-field input,
  .form-field textarea {
    font-family: var(--font-main);
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    background: var(--bg-subtle);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color var(--transition);
    resize: vertical;
  }

  .form-field input:focus,
  .form-field textarea:focus {
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .form-field input::placeholder,
  .form-field textarea::placeholder {
    color: var(--text-subtle);
  }

  .feedback-success {
    display: none;
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .form-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
